
! Aurorials Slitaz (Pack) Theme
! By: HolkFoor (https://twitter.com/holkfoor)
! Version: 1.0-20130703

========================================================

1. Aurorials Slim Theme

a) Install Slim Theme
   Directory: /usr/share/slim/themes

b) Config Slim Theme
   File: /etc/slim.conf
   Line: current_theme

========================================================

2. Aurorials GTK2 & Openbox Themes

a) Important Notice!
   Aurorials depends on murrine engine.

b) Install GTK2 & Openbox
   Directory: /usr/share/themes
   Optional : /home/$USER/.themes

========================================================

3. Aurorials Wallpaper

a) You can install the wallpaper in some directory. 
   Or install in /usr/share/backgrounds

========================================================

  Thank you for using Aurorials theme.
